{"id": "1513465126924058634", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》新OST已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处**\n有一种叫蒲公英的植物，会让种子乘着风漂流。\n毛绒绒的种子随风流浪，离开故土好远好远。\n它孤身一人，会在什么时候决定自己的归宿呢？\n那就是，沙漠中有唯一的一个人爱着那株蒲公英的时候。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n企划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens new OST was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens × Saya no Uta OST┊Saya EP: Where the Dandelions Go**\nThere is a plant called the dandelion, which lets its seeds drift away upon the wind.\nThe downy seeds wander wherever the wind carries them, far, so very far from the soil that bore them.\nWhen does such a lonely seed decide where it belongs?\n...It is the moment when, somewhere in the desert, one single person happens to love that dandelion.\n\nProject: B.I.A.V. Studio\nComposer: F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:50:05.081000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "Ramona_love", "emoji_id": "1459077541829546007", "count": 8}, {"emoji": "Saya_yum", "emoji_id": "1513124263291387975", "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465127314264204", "filename": "c8bbaf0adc87f25e.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1474011, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465127314264204/c8bbaf0adc87f25e.png?ex=6a27d3bd&is=6a26823d&hm=332711365dd0bae5c2e708d96324a552016900a583ca08022d125bd7a8935d05&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"], "is_thread_starter": true}
{"id": "1513465361717133423", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01. 忘却之歌-Song of Memento-Emi Evans Ver.**\n\n「我能呼唤你的名字吗？即使世界消逝。」\n如果回忆都将湮灭消散，漆黑的遗忘将吞噬所有未及缅怀的往事。\n那就牵起手来吧，让银色的光辉链接你我。\n在崭新的幻梦中，在柔嫩的种子萌发的早春时节。\n\n\"May I call your name? Though the world all fades...\"\nIf all memories are doomed to dissolve into nothing, and pitch-black oblivion devours every unmourned moment of the past—\nthen take my hand, and let a silver radiance bind us together.\nIn a newborn dream, in the early spring when tender seeds first sprout.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:51:01.060000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:51:37.316000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465361692098591", "filename": "01._-Song_of_Memento-Emi_Evans_Ver..wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 73384520, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465361692098591/01._-Song_of_Memento-Emi_Evans_Ver..wav?ex=6a27d3f5&is=6a268275&hm=75a3be0ce67b6b1e26e7234fe64e9df2ebe0897e2a69566fb579470b6e41274a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1513465418730438846", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02. 忘却之歌-Song of Memento-いとうかなこ Ver.**\n\n「能听见我的声音吗？即使身影消融在风中。」\n风中传来遥远的呼唤，那是跨越遥远的时间，从广阔而寒冷的冬夜，忘却的彼岸传来的探寻之声。\n\n\"May you hear me call, even as my shadow fades into thin air.\"\nA distant cry drifts upon the wind—a searching voice, traversing vast stretches of time, calling from a wide and frigid winter night, from the far shore of oblivion.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:51:14.653000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465418126458940", "filename": "02._-Song_of_Memento-_Ver..wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 73374920, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465418126458940/02._-Song_of_Memento-_Ver..wav?ex=6a27d402&is=6a268282&hm=9195f82c118ba77783c28e766e9635ea4b9ba299a34c84b36b1969b056be9ce1&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1513465599659999393", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03. 原罪-Original Sin**\n\n一切生命带着无知降生，自万物中汲取养料，改造环境，掠夺资源，供养自我。\n这是无可逃避的原罪。\n\nAll life is born into ignorance, drawing sustenance from the world, reshaping its surroundings, plundering its resources to nourish the self.\nSuch is the original sin from which none can escape.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:51:57.790000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465599542427710", "filename": "03._-Original_Sin.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 35426120, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465599542427710/03._-Original_Sin.wav?ex=6a27d42d&is=6a2682ad&hm=ea0d835cd72432ae8b61ac36618813f9f6f29b5375a8a79fff9895109faed453&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1513465631507222598", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04. 四重回忆-Quartlet of Recollections**\n\n回忆闪烁交叠，结局真伪不明。\n但这真的重要吗？\n毕竟，未必所有的故事都以爱作为开头，但都将以死亡作为终点。\n\nMemories flicker and overlap; the truth of their endings remains uncertain.\nBut does it truly matter?\nAfter all, not every story begins with love... yet every one of them ends in death.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:52:05.383000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465630345658458", "filename": "04._-Quartlet_of_Recollections.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 15323720, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465630345658458/04._-Quartlet_of_Recollections.wav?ex=6a27d435&is=6a2682b5&hm=b6a368ddb4ae475f5dd4bbd386a59833516b843ffc4d2a3421988014c8c78a06&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1513465701338452040", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05. 血域-Vista in Red**\n\n你是否也厌倦了普通的、循环的、乏味的、日复一日的生活？\n来点新鲜的吧，另一个视界正敞开血盆大口，向你发出欢迎的邀约。\n\nHave you, too, grown weary of the ordinary, cyclical, tedious days that bleed into one another?\nThen taste something new: another world yawns open its blood-red maw, extending its welcoming invitation to you.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:52:22.032000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465701023748208", "filename": "05._-Vista_in_Red.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 34245320, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465701023748208/05._-Vista_in_Red.wav?ex=6a27d445&is=6a2682c5&hm=4fec0c65187a0eb03c9166986230a5e33e9928ca8dd9e1bd592ced5407efc64d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1513465751913369671", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06. 奇迹-A Miracle**\n\n如果有一天，你也和我一样，陷入血肉模糊、腐臭糜烂的光景。\n那么你也一定能够理解——\n与她的小巧指尖触碰的瞬间，是人世间不可多得的奇迹。\n\nIf one day you, like me, find yourself sunk into a vision of mangled flesh and putrid decay...\nthen surely you, too, will understand:\nthat fleeting moment when her delicate fingertips brushed against mine... It was a miracle scarcely found anywhere.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:52:34.090000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465751607050331", "filename": "06._-A_Miracle.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 49634120, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465751607050331/06._-A_Miracle.wav?ex=6a27d452&is=6a2682d2&hm=34edd31a8bb2b21a2d51ca730df9df2a23ef3df667b6ad90edb5d735095905ee&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1513465802425110579", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07. 沙海漫游-Roaming the Dunes**\n\n广阔天地，茫茫沙海。\n那是只有你我的无人之境。\n那是永恒自由的爱之漫游。\n\nA boundless world, an endless sea of sand.\nA no-man's-land that belongs to none but you and me.\nAn eternal, unfettered odyssey of love.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:52:46.133000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465801963864114", "filename": "07._-Roaming_the_Dunes.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 30789320, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465801963864114/07._-Roaming_the_Dunes.wav?ex=6a27d45e&is=6a2682de&hm=81e619b360ec35b8eb359009a4ef494370f5ff6bedd44c64ae320fd3c92c2507&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1513465898265219174", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**08. 无罪的暴虐-Vindicated Vice**\n\n被无法理解、无法辨识、令人作呕的畸形之物逼近时，发起防御式攻击是生物的本能。\n因此，这不能算作罪孽。\n\nWhen confronted by something incomprehensible, unrecognizable, a nauseating aberration drawing near—to lash out in defense is the instinct of every living creature.\nAnd so, it cannot be counted as sin.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:53:08.983000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465897849979040", "filename": "08._-Vindicated_Vice.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 54002120, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465897849979040/08._-Vindicated_Vice.wav?ex=6a27d474&is=6a2682f4&hm=9d5737246fe79343451a72e0db837606f477ff0ed90fc6c92210fca258057711&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1513465995564548146", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**09. 雨季-Rainy Season**\n\n爱是崇高，爱是贪婪；爱是赐福，爱是诅咒。\n爱随水而生，亦将随水而逝。\n而雨季不再来。\n\nLove is sublime; love is avarice. Love is benediction; love is malediction.\nLove is born of water, and with the water shall it pass away.\nAnd this rainy season will not come again.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:53:32.181000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513465994960703572", "filename": "09._-Rainy_Season.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 39861318, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513465994960703572/09._-Rainy_Season.wav?ex=6a27d48c&is=6a26830c&hm=26b6f164735522bead0ad09577f901ddace670644184cdd1037cc8ee1fe3e360&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1513466054419157043", "channel_id": "1513465126924058634", "type": 0, "author_id": "1485258210209435701", "author_name": "morimensstaff06", "author_bot": false, "content": "**10. 揭幕颂歌-Hymn of the Unveiling\n**\n高歌吧，闪耀的生命正赞颂自由，将希望的羽种播撒至遍及之地。\nSing aloud! For radiant life now extols its freedom, scattering the feathered seeds of hope to every corner of the earth.", "timestamp": "2026-06-08T08:53:46.213000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1513466054091866165", "filename": "10._-Hymn_of_the_Unveiling.wav", "content_type": "audio/wav", "size": 35234118, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1513465126924058634/1513466054091866165/10._-Hymn_of_the_Unveiling.wav?ex=6a27d49a&is=6a26831a&hm=a77ad8a2cdbaf2ebaa8ca13bb2c8b8d44b79556e5e2af5a65828751433d78d4c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1513465126924058634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜×沙耶之歌OST：沙耶EP·蒲公英去往何处", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
